'''The Great Black Dick Hoax''' is one of the most elaborate and massive scams in the [[history]] of [[mankind]]. Those spreading the myth claim that black people have the biggest dicks around and are therefore better than your average [[white]] man. As we, the good editors at [[Encyclopedia Dramatica]] will establish, this is complete [[bullshit]].

== Greatest Hoax Ever? ==
