This is one of the greatest hoaxes of our time. The idea that black people have huge dicks is so widely believed that it out-ranks [[religion]] in our increasingly [[atheism|atheistic]] world. It also shows no signs of slowing down, being spread by [[MTV]] and other pop culture outlets, it has left a lasting [[scar]] on the [[American]] conscience and has been mistakenly established as [[fact]]. This while the person with the biggest dick in the world is a white American male, named [[Pretty Cool Guy|Jonah Falcon]]. He holds the Guinness Book of Records title of the man with the largest dick alive. His dick measures 9.5 inches (24 cm) in length when flaccid and 13.5 inches (34 cm) in length when erect.

== The Perfect Scam ==

Those who circulate this rumor are surprisingly crafty about this entire scam, showing an animal cunning. They realize that they are a small enough minority that only the filthiest [[slut]] or the most [[Mature|experienced]] [[prostitute]] could possibly [[fuck]] enough niggers to get an accurate sense the actual size of the black person dick. This means that the dicks depicted in the fake pornography detailed in Exhibit A provide the most common object of reference for whites' perceptions of this hoax, allowing any black person to claim to have the biggest dick in town and fuck any [[trailer trash]] [[jailbait]] [[slut]] he wants to. [[Some argue]] that this is just [[retard|retards]] who don't know that [[math|small differences in the mean manifest as large differences at the tails]].

