The only evidence cited is [[pornography]] that only [[faggots]] buy because the dicks usually take up the entire fucking screen. But as you can see from Exhibit A, these seemingly massive members are just fake dicks made from some unidentified material.

[[truth|Furthermore, if blacks had as huge dicks as they claim to have,  then they would end up killing the women they rape]], [[guro]]-style. If they really did have huge six foot long dicks, there would be nobody to testify against them for rape because they would be nothing but [[Babypaste|womanpaste]] smeared all over a cock. This would mean the percentage of blacks in [[jail]] would be lower than 80% because nobody would ever learn of or know about the rape- because they'd be dead. But the percentage is still high, proving this to be a hoax and nothing more. [[Proof|QED]].

